---
source: crates/ship-policy/src/help.rs
expression: "wrong_tool_help(AgentRole::Captain, None, \"captain_merge\")"
---
`captain_merge` is not available during no active task. Accept the mate's work and merge

Available actions:
- `captain_assign` — Assign a task to your mate
- `captain_git_status` — Check git status of the session worktree
- `code` — Read, search, edit files, run commands, commit
- `web_search` — Search the web
